Description:
When entering the bandit camp you see a really big werewolf yelling and giving orders to other werewolves. He noticies your presence and looks at you with a mocking face.

That's Yogger, the butcher of Senenthia, and he has been terrorizing the Senenthia forest for a long time.

It's time to put a stop to Yogger and disperse the bandits once and for all.
DescriptionAction: Running away now would only make things worse.
